Install Apache Web Server-EC2.
Type following commands on terminal
>sudo dnf update -y
>sudo dnf install httpd -y
>sudo systemctl start httpd
>sudo systemctl enable httpd
 Now Apache is installed!!
 Copy public IPv4 address
 Paste it in browser
 For website-EC2
 >sudo yum update -y
 >sudo yum install httpd -y
 >sudo systemctl start httpd
 >sudo systemctl enable httpd
 Apache is now running
 Now create simple website
 Type command
 > sudo nano /var/www/html/index.html
This opens text editor
Now type html code
Press ctrl+O =>Enter=>ctrl+X
Then copy public IPv4 address and run
